svg.text: A Multi-Tenant SaaS for Agencies & Freelancers.
FlowShan is a cinematic project management system focused on speed and fluid transitions.
It bridges local-first guest usage with cloud-synced team collaboration.
• State-Linked Transitions: Complex layout morphing with LayoutGroup
• Hybrid Persistence: 5s undo/restore for non-destructive soft-deletes
• Smart Notify: Telegram / Email / Push multi-channel engine
